ormation. Resonium Calcium (calcium polystyrene sulfonate)." Sanofi-Synthelabo Canada Inc, Markham, ON.[5] "Product Information. Kayexalate (sodium polystyrene sulfonate)." Sanofi Winthrop Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[7] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767369485);
